</P>
<P>
MANILA -- A group of armed men shot and killed an American
national in an ambush Monday in a province north of Manila,
police said.
</P>
<P>
This developed as policemen and soldiers braced for terrorist
attacks on American targets by Muslims sympathetic to Saudi
billionaire Osama Bin Laden whom the United States suspected of
ordering the bombing of U.S. embassies in Kenya and Tanzania.
(Philippines-American Killed)
</P>
