projects with foreign investors, valued at 300 million US dollars,
he said, adding that many foreign investors showed interest in
basic industries in the western part of China.
</P>
<P>
Some 785 large and medium-sized Chinese enterprises and over
4,000 business people from 29 countries and regions attended the
eight-day fair. 
