<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese People's
Association for Friendship with Foreign Countries (CPAFFC) and
the Sino-DPRK Friendship Association held a reception here this
evening at the Great Hall of People to mark the 50th anniversary
of the founding of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea
(DPRK).
</P>
<P>
More than 140 Chinese and DPRK guests attended the banquet,
including Jiang Chunyun, vice-chairman of the Standing Committee
of the Chinese National People's Congress, and Zhao Nanqi,
vice-chairman of the National Committee of the Chinese People's
Political Consultative Conference.
</P>
