<TEXT>
<P>
Third, efforts will be made to develop consumer goods of
different grades and to expand the services market so as to meet
the needs of different consumers. Meanwhile, the production of
marketable agricultural production materials and rural daily
necessities will be expanded, and the urban-rural commodity
distribution system invigorated in an effort to further tap the
potential of the rural market.
</P>
<P>
Fourth, the export structure will be further improved so as
to further raise the quality, grade and added-value of export
commodities.
</P>
<P>
Wu, who used to be China's foreign trade minister, stressed the
necessity of optimizing the overall export structure by increasing
the export of high-value-added and high-tech products as well as
