great importance to improving the quality and grade of the
traditional export commodities, and to developing and exporting
more brand-name items.
</P>
<P>
Fifth, the reform of the foreign trade system will be deepened
so as to further tap its potential, improve its management,
readjust the market strategy in a timely fashion, and lower the
costs and sharpen the competitive edge of the foreign trade
companies.
</P>
<P>
Sixth, the investment environment will be steadfastly improved
and overseas investment will be more actively attracted.
</P>
<P>
Wu told the meeting that, apart from measures that have already
been taken such as announcing guidance for industries welcoming
overseas investment and tariff breaks for imports by
overseas-funded enterprises, the Chinese government plans to
further simplify the approval procedures for overseas-funded
projects and take more steps to stop the random charging of fees
from overseas-funded enterprises.  
