<HEADLINE> Xinhua Stock Index Change Mixed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Today's Xinhua A stock
index fell by 0.87 point to close at 136.77, and the Xinhua B
stock index climbed 0.15 point to finish at 27.44.
</P>
<P>
The Xinhua Stock index is China's first national unitary
stock exponent, which is jointly designed and issued by the
Economic Information Department of the Xinhua News Agency and
Beijing University.  
</P>
