<HEADLINE> Bank Allocates 20 Billion Yuan to Aid Poor Students </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- The Construction Bank of China
(CBC) announced here today that it has allocated 20 billion yuan
(2.4 billion US dollars) to aid college students from the flooded
areas who are having difficulties financing their college
education.
</P>
<P>
