over 230 billion yuan (27.8 billion US dollars) to the Yangtze
River Valley and the Nenjiang River Valley, both heavily hit by
devastating floods this summer.
</P>
<P>
Since 1996, the CBC has allocated 20 billion yuan each year to
aid more than 1,000 needy college students, the spokesman said.
