<P>
Sabah (Morning)
</P>
<P>
-- Addressing a welcoming ceremony upon his arrival in
Jerusalem for a two-day visit on Monday, Turkish Prime Minister
Mesut Yilmaz stressed that the rapidly growing military
cooperation between Turkey and Israel is by no means directed
against any third party.
</P>
<P>
